 [ ] Treasury repair assigned if needed
Do in Simba
Update Treasury Setup, Ledger View, and Treasury Summary.

Chapter 7: Strengthen the Meeting Rhythm
Core Question
Can we keep returning?
Understand
A society is only as strong as its rhythm of return.
Meetings are not just events.
They are where memory, decision, repair, and assignment happen.
A meeting rhythm should be realistic enough to keep and strong enough to maintain momentum.
If meetings are too frequent, people burn out.
If they are too rare, the society drifts.
The next container needs a meeting rhythm that matches the work.
Discuss
Did we meet consistently?
Were meetings useful?
Did meetings produce decisions?
Did notes get saved?
Did assignments get completed?
What rhythm fits the next container?
Build: Meeting Rhythm Review
