PART THREE: CHOOSE THE NEXT CONTAINER

Chapter 8: Choose One Growth Path
Core Question
What can we now carry responsibly?
Understand
The next container is not everything.
It is one disciplined growth path.
Choose one path based on:
Evidence from Day 100
 Member capacity
 Needs Map
 Skills and Assets Map
 Treasury strength
 Care team readiness
 Role clarity
 Community urgency
 Solvability
The society should not choose the most impressive path.
It should choose the path it can actually carry.
Discuss
What does the Day 100 Report point toward?
What need repeated most clearly?
What capacity do we actually have?
What are we not ready for?
What next container would strengthen the whole society?
