 [ ] Eligibility defined
 [ ] Aid limits set
 [ ] Approval process clarified
 [ ] Privacy rule confirmed
 [ ] Reserve goal set
Do in Simba
Connect this container to Mutual Aid Operations, Treasury, Ledger, and Aid Request workflow.

Chapter 10: Business Support Container
Core Question
Can we help businesses through organized circulation?
Understand
Businesses are not the root.
They are the fruit.
The Business Support Container helps the society organize customers, campaigns, referrals, institutional purchasing, youth apprenticeships, and business support with accountability.
This container should not become favoritism.
It should support businesses through clear criteria, disclosed relationships, measurable campaigns, and reports.
