Chapter 11: Property Stewardship Container
Core Question
Can we protect what the community already owns?
Understand
Land is time made visible.
The Property Stewardship Container helps the society organize property education, document protection, tax awareness, deed review referrals, heirs property awareness, church property stewardship, home repair support, or vacant land mapping.
This container requires strong privacy.
Property information can expose family conflict, debt, ownership vulnerability, or legal risk.
Start with education, documents, trusted referrals, and stewardship.
