Chapter 12: Youth Formation Container
Core Question
Can we train youth into real responsibility?
Understand
Youth should not only perform.
They should learn to govern.
The Youth Formation Container creates roles, mentorship, skill-building, opportunity funds, apprenticeships, technology projects, history projects, preparedness training, and leadership practice.
Youth should have real outputs with adult support.
The goal is not youth decoration.
The goal is youth formation.
