Chapter 13: Preparedness Container
Core Question
Can we prepare before crisis?
Understand
Preparedness is mutual aid before emergency.
The Preparedness Container helps the society organize communication trees, elder check-ins, emergency supplies, evacuation planning, document backups, transportation, medicine access, food and water readiness, and care teams.
Preparedness is not fear.
It is organized care before pressure arrives.
