Chapter 14: Leadership Training Container
Core Question
Can the society outlive the original builders?
Understand
Institutions outlive individuals because leadership is trained, shared, documented, and rotated.
A society becomes fragile when only one or two people know how things work.
The Leadership Training Container prepares new facilitators, recordkeepers, treasurers, care coordinators, liaisons, and project leads.
Leadership is not title.
Leadership is responsibility that can be taught and transferred.
