How do we build the next container without losing the first?
Understand
The next 90 days should deepen the society’s capacity.
Do not abandon the first container.
Keep:
Meetings
 Ledger
 Rules
 Care Teams
 Reports
 Recommitment
 Privacy
 Treasury discipline
The next container adds one focused growth path on top of the foundation.
