Final Principle
The next container is not about becoming impressive.
It is about becoming more dependable.
The first container proved the soil could hold seed.
The next container asks whether the roots can go deeper.
Build deeper before you build bigger.
Return before you recruit.
Repair before you scale.
Report before you celebrate.
And always remember:
We have not built everything. We are learning how to build what can last.

